The '''Olimpíada Brasileira de Matemática''' is a mathematics competition held every year for students of [[Brazil]]. The participants are awarded gold, silver and bronze medals in accordance with their performance. The main purpose of this competition is to help in selecting students to represent [[Brazil]] at the [[International Mathematical Olympiad]].

