The '''Richard Dimbleby Lecture''' (also known as the '''Dimbleby Lecture''') was founded in memory of [[Richard Dimbleby]], the [[BBC]] [[Television presenter|broadcaster]]. It has been delivered by an influential business or political figure almost every year since 1972 (with gaps in 1981, 1991, 1993 and 2008).
